data.name: lblDeluxeDesc.Text
data.value: A deluxe room is usually larger than a standard room and comes with additional amenities such as a larger TV, a mini-fridge, and a safe. The rate for a deluxe room could range from PHP 6,000 per night.

data.name: lblExecutiveDesc.Text
data.value: An Executive Room is usually designed for business travelers and comes with a separate workspace and additional amenities such as a fax machine and printer. The rate for an Executive Room could range from PHP 15,000 per night.
